    <statement>
        <p>
            Kiran puts $400 a month in her retirement account that amazingly also earns 7% interest compounded monthly. Use the <xref ref="future-value-annuity-formula" text="title"/> to determine how much Kiran will have in her retirement account in 28 years.
        </p>
        <ol marker="(a)">
            <li>
                <p>
                    In the formula, what number should we use for <m>p</m>?
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    In the formula, what number should we use for <m>r</m>?
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    In the formula, what number should we use for <m>y</m>?
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Plug everything in and evaluate to find Kiran's retirement account balance after 28 years.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </statement>
</activity>